Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 17
Set Width 1360
Set Height 940
Set Padding 28
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=/Users/xm1k3/tools/personal/skai:$PATH" Enter
Type "cd /tmp && rm -rf skai-gif && mkdir skai-gif && cd skai-gif" Enter
Type "PROMPT='%F{45}skai%f %F{245}$%f '" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 700ms
Type "skai stats" Sleep 400ms Enter
Sleep 3800ms

Type "clear" Sleep 200ms Enter
Type "skai info pdf" Sleep 400ms Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "clear" Sleep 200ms Enter
Type "skai install pdf --target claude-code --project" Sleep 400ms Enter
Sleep 2500ms
Type "y" Sleep 300ms Enter
Sleep 3200ms

Hide
Type "cd /tmp && rm -rf skai-gif" Enter
Show
